<Body NumberFormat="default">
<P1group id="p00003">
<Title><?start-line?>Civil penalties for non-payment of TV licence fee</Title>
<P1>
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<P2>
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>Section 363 (licence required for use of TV receiver) of the Communications Act <?new-line?>2003 is amended as follows.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>In subsections (2) and (3), for “guilty of an offence” substitute “is guilty of a <?new-line?>civil offence”.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>Leave out subsection (4) and insert—</Text>
<BlockAmendment TargetClass="primary" Context="main" TargetSubClass="unknown" Format="double">
<P2>
<Pnumber>4</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>A person guilty of a civil offence under this section shall be liable to a <?new-line?>penalty charge.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>4A</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>The Secretary of State shall specify by regulations subject to affirmative <?new-line?>resolution by the House of Commons the levels of charges to be <?new-line?>imposed under this section.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
</BlockAmendment>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
</P1>
</P1group>
<P1group id="p00004">
<Title><?start-line?>Short title, commencement and extent</Title>
<P1>
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<P2>
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>This Act may be cited as the BBC Licence Fee (Civil Debt) Act 2013.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>This Act shall come into force on 1 January 2017.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>This Act extends to England and Wales, Scotland and Northern Ireland.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
</P1>
</P1group>
